{"hb6e1c559g1cc3g4ad6ga503g0ead85ff0e9f": ["Urgh, that smells ripe.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "ce74317b-2b4f-5e49-95ab-2e2e895fb81f"], "h7c64b99eg760bg4600gbc6dg774b3d31a586": ["Urgh. That body's so ripe, I'd need to drink the blood with a fork.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h747dcc0bg8373g46e0gadc5gd4fc33bbd804": ["| Oh no. He is rot. |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h31ebd3f9g3f39g4117ga320g8660579b4689": ["Ugh. That corpse is riper than a Minauros bog.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h8a754251g254dg4aeeg9c82g6f8a3d448dfa": ["The rot of death. <i>Delightful.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "hbe26890cg0467g409fg9189g49b659f3b6f8": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h7ab966fag2a91g4c9cg9c5bg2f56665be11d": ["That corpse smells ripe. Enough time for its killer to have moved on...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h686ed75cg4f72g46f0g9516g08faf3314ab6": ["Gods, this assault on the nostrils should be labelled a war crime.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h6e90a252g0551g4a01gac78gbcaa05791b9a": ["Ugh. I'll never get used to the stench of death.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"], "h9ffd8696g3e2eg47a1gbb8dg3a2666faaab4": ["Ugh, that stench. Body must have been here a good while.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_KarlachRecruitmentTollhouse_PAD_CorpseSmell.html", "73f61f8c-b65f-d303-c9ed-c618e9ae7fd2"]}